{"word":"H7830 - שַׁחַץ - shachats - shakh'-ats - [idiom] lion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שַׁחַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shachats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shakh'-ats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] lion"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அகங்காரம், துஷ்டமிருகம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"dignity, pride; majestic wild animals"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From an unused root apparently meaning to <i>strut</i>; <i>haughtiness</i> (as evinced by the attitude): -  X lion, pride."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7830 - שַׁחַץ - shachats - shakh'-ats/7830\">H7830</a>, <a href=\"#/H7831 - שַׁחֲצֹום - Shachătsôwm - shakh-ats-ome'/7831\">H7831</a>"}]}